content: I'm having a deja vu here but I think the test cases with a ton of junk ignorable characters are completely unneeded. Maybe leave 1 or 2 max, but 14 is just silly. Even better would be to remove anything other than brackets in the inputs and not insult the people solving the puzzle with  pointless distractions.

The harder version of Brackets Enhanced.

The greedy heuristic doesn't work here, we're back to full non-deterministic matching the way Brackets Extended was intended.
